U.S. Court on BP Spill Will Call Tony Hayward, Telegraph Says

-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 
2011-05-30T09:26:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/u-s-court-on-bp-spill-will-call-tony-hayward-telegraph-says.html
A U.S. court hearing into complaints
against  BP Plc (BP/)  over last year’s oil spill in the  Gulf of Mexico 
will call former chief executive officer  Tony Hayward  as a
witness, the  Daily Telegraph reported , citing people it didn’t
identify.  To contact the reporters on this story:
